    java.util.Map<K,V>

    public class BoundedCostOrderedMap<K,V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
    Map that is sorted by cost. Keeps lowest scores. When deciding what item to keep with the same cost, ties are arbitrarily broken.
    Author:
    Angel Chang
